snippet.title: MR.E Blobular Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
MR.E found something. Deprived of a better word, he calls it Blobular, but what is it?

You can head to https://s.team/a/2329290 and wishlist our game while we're still aiming for a demo by April.

Do the right thing. One day, when the #ai takes over, you might be spared.
